e8","tid":1359751,"uid":29880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:44:40.000Z","msg":"我都係,冇野好輸<br />\n供緊樓嗰啲就..."},{"pid":"b79322db31cb3e7bc059d0c750f9d26f4112dd28","tid":1359751,"uid":210794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:44:42.000Z","msg":"屌㩒錯負皮⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n講真，出老解佢仆街先"},{"pid":"c4426e2e275252646a89834bc8dee71d10816016","tid":1359751,"uid":38745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:46:16.000Z","msg":"民不畏死 奈何以死懼之<br />\n<br />\n推呀屌！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KdAqEQH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKdAqEQH.png&h=9b40f637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>727元朗集中反黑</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">香港人絕不向黑勢力低頭！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但係！記住！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求！缺！一！不！可！<br />\n香港人！不！撤！不！散！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>義士不是condom！<br />\n說好的一個都不能少！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/01iorVB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F01iorVB.png&h=b7815076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑警於721，無人衝擊、毫無預警下<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>開槍</strong></span></span>！<br />\n總共開咗<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">36槍！</span></span><br />\n<em><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係開槍！唔係扔彈呀！</span></strong></em><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>如果呢啖氣你都忍到嘅話，咁6月12號仲平乜撚嘢反？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求！</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n二、釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n三、撤回612暴動定性<br />\n四、追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n五、立即實行雙普選，還我真香港！</span><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W16xijK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW16xijK.png&h=9fb73358&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mXaewEN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmXaewEN.png&h=6e7eb5c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff462231a8a40c5d8705752c1d3a12abf58786a0","tid":1359751,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"599b0bcb1f7b9ebb0582a2d566b028fbe83f2fad","tid":1359751,"uid":117412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:01:10.000Z","msg":"我地唔係塞幾舊錢就收口既中國豬<br />\n既然儲極錢都買唔到樓<br />\n係香港生活慘過食屎<br />\n根本係死局喇 唔推翻邊有用<br />\n冇自由寧願死<br />\n快d出老解<br />\n大家一齊攬抄<br />\n換黎香港重光<br />\n<br />\n我諗正評支持出老解會過萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持請正皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:46:46.000Z","msg":"又呃正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b753b4875a15d4d84176c008037cff350a4f4f42","tid":1359751,"uid":151507,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:47:06.000Z","msg":"今年買左樓，月入過5萬支持焦土<br />\n與其睇住自己家園一點一滴比人敗壞<br />\n我寧願親手了結佢，都唔想下一代生活係一個咁的地方"},{"pid":"bddae77e45b882451509a2b43739a0b5282e2894","tid":1359751,"uid":57674,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b753b4875a15d4d84176c008037cff350a4f4f42","tid":1359751,"uid":151507,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:47:06.000Z","msg":"今年買左樓，月入過5萬支持焦土<br />\n與其睇住自己家園一點一滴比人敗壞<br />\n我寧願親手了結佢，都唔想下一代生活係一個咁的地方"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T08:48:16.000Z","msg":"same 供緊樓 6皮月入 支持焦土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee2e7b9b11212fd3781af95847cb894bc